title: 820-3209 No power
message:
Don't waste time checking iGPU voltage; we explained so many times on the forum why.

As PLT_RESET_L comes on, power on sequence is completed.
Now may only have a communication issue on some bus, BIOS, or bad CPU, RAM.

Did you check USB activity?
Connect speaker, in case of RAM error beeps.
